<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Home Page</title>

    <!-- STYESHEETS-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/vendor/normalize-4.1.1.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/vendor/border-box.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/layout.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/nav.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/footer.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/products.css" type="text/css" />

    <!--FONTS-->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alata&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Caslon+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!--SCRIPTS-->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/vendor/jquery-3.0.0.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/app.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav>
      <%- include("./partials/_nav") %>
    </nav>

    <main class = "container">
      <!--About us section-->
      <div class="about-us">
        <h2>New swapper? No problem!</h2>
        <h4>register today and get your first 3 plants for free</h4>

        <div class="info-cards">
          <!--card 1: plant it-->
          <div class="about-card">
            <h3>sign up</h3>
            <p>If you're new to swapping, it's easy to become a swapper! Simply register for an account and you're good to get started on your very own swapping journey.</p>
          </div>

          <!--card 2: swap it-->
          <div class="about-card">
            <h3>swap</h3>
            <p>Browse our site as much as you'd like! Once you've found that perfect plant that you'd like to swap with, simply message the seller with our handy-dandy chat feature to start the swap.</p>
          </div>

          <!--card 3: grow it-->
          <div class="about-card">
            <h3>shop</h3>
            <p>Our motto here is plant it, swap it, grow it! After your first few swaps, you will have mastered the art of swapping. Continue to shop, swap, and stay connected with us on social media!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1>Featured Items</h1>
      <div class="featured-products">
        <!--List of featured items-->
        <% for (const product of products) { %>
        <!--product 1-->
        <div>
          <a href="/product/<%=product.id%>"">
            <div class="product-listing">
              <img src="<%=product.thumbnail_image_url%>" alt="fasciata" style="width:100%">
              <h4><%=product.title%></h4>
              <form method="POST" action="/product/<%= product.id %>">
              <button type="submit" class="btn">
                Favourite
              </button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h1>Our picks for you</h1>
        <div class="featured-products">
          <!--List of more featured products-->

          <!--product 1-->
          <div>
            <a href="/product/6">
              <div class="product-listing">
                <img img src="/docs/pots/pot-2.jpg" alt="macrame" style="width:100%">
                <h4>macrame pot</h4>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">
                  Favourite
                </button>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>

          <!--product 4-->
          <div>
            <a href="/product/4">
              <div class="product-listing">
                <img img src="/docs/plants/plant-3.jpg" alt="pinkroses" style="width:100%">
                <h4>pink roses</h4>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">
                  Favourite
                </button>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>

          <!--product 2-->
          <div>
            <a href="/product/1">
              <div class="product-listing">
                <img img src="/docs/plants/plant-1.jpg" alt="fasciata" style="width:100%">
                <h4>fasciata</h4>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">
                  Favourite
                </button>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>

          <!--product 2-->
          <div>
            <a href="/product/2">
              <div class="product-listing">
                <img img src="/docs/pots/pot-1.jpg" alt="earthpot" style="width:100%">
                <h4>earth pot</h4>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">
                  Favourite
                </button>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>

          <!--product 3-->
          <div>
            <a href="/product/3">
              <div class="product-listing">
                <img img src="/docs/plants/plant-2.jpg" alt="rubbertree" style="width:100%">
                <h4>rubber tree</h4>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">
                  Favourite
                </button>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!--About us section-->
        <div class="about-us">
          <h2>About Us</h2>

          <div class="info-cards">
            <!--card 1: plant it-->
            <div class="about-card">
              <h3>plant it</h3>
              <p>A Plant Swap is simply an event where fellow plant owners can come together to swap their plants. This could be done anywhere—like someone's home, a public park or community garden, a church or community center, or even a local business.</p>
            </div>

            <!--card 2: swap it-->
            <div class="about-card">
              <h3>swap it</h3>
              <p>The rules are simple: bring a pest-free, beautiful plant, or two or three for trade; they can be potted or bare root—as long as you’re prepared to part with them.</p>
            </div>

            <!--card 3: grow it-->
            <div class="about-card">
              <h3>grow it</h3>
              <p>Swap what you've brought, and take home a lot! Keep up the spirit of the trade, you never know what you can find out there. Take home your newly adopted plants and watch them grow!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <%- include("./partials/_footer") %>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
